It would still be advisable for users to exercise caution when interacting with any new domain, even if no immediate signs of malicious activity are present.

In conclusion, based on the available WHOIS information, I would print: "The domain is not malicious." Nonetheless, keep in mind that thorough due diligence should always be conducted before engaging with any online platform.
